spec_data.Name: jlibrtp
spec_data.Description:
jlibrtp aims to create a library that makes it easy to support
RTP (RFC 3550,3551) in Java applications. SRTP (RFC 3771) has been
delayed in favor of RFC 4585.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Wed 26 Jul 2017 07:28:38 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Java library for the Real-Time Transport Protocol (RTP)
